{"tid":2210623,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"奇文分享：從香島中學學生因政見被重罰 反思教協建立人權校園的空白和失敗","createTime":"2020-09-20T14:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T10:37:38.000Z","uid":276028,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ece8d424231225480dc88ac927d35fc374c43a","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/sc/education/hkptu202001a/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Fsc%2Feducation%2Fhkptu202001a%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=49902fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/sc/education/hkptu202001a/</a><br />\n<br />\n驚訝！原來學生的權利和自由受到剝削，並非是香島中學特有？<br />\n教協多年來提倡民主自由，竟然漠視學生的自由和人權被學校長期剝削？<br />\n學生為反送中運動為民主付出犧牲，但是教協和黃絲老師回到學校後，繼繼雙重標準剝判學生的人權？<br />\n教協漠視學校的懲治權過大，可以任意魚肉學生？<br />\n教協對人權校園政綱空白？<br />\n若果你是教協會長，應如何改善學生權益？"},{"pid":"fe879fcfe739a66b2e932653b7d69b038036944e","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"果然藍絲痴線佬賤視學生的人權和自由，立即負評。"},{"pid":"47269390d5e439a10d8c08b638a1b34c115687ba","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"71a095f473ede597f25a912aa23aa6bca1e309cd","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:27:30.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"8e8be9ed1f2c0a04bc16ea68dbe32f49c4b533d5","tid":2210623,"uid":53122,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"教怯係園工超市福利會之類<br />\n<br />\n點會做到嘢"},{"pid":"980576f9de05605f0275dd967cf8a66b648da962","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"07b761ab5b0f57d08be5ee5ced85af668bc79e13","tid":2210623,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"